				<title>MyBatis 插件机制：Interceptor 原理与自定义插件</title>
				<link>https://liwenqikeep.github.io/posts/mybatis-%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6interceptor-%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</link>
